OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FA 60-year-old British tourist is among
OL,8,F21 people charged under the United
OL,9,FArab Emirates' (UAE) cybercrime laws
OL,10,Fin connection with videos and social
OL,11,Fmedia posts about recent Iranian drone
OL,12,Fand missile strikes.
OL,14,FThe man, who has not been named, said
OL,15,Fhe deleted the video from his phone
OL,16,Fimmediately when asked to and had no
OL,17,Fintention of doing anything wrong,
OL,18,Faccording to the legal advocacy group
OL,19,FDetained in Dubai.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FNonetheless, he has found himself
OL,8,Fcaught up in a wider group of charges
OL,9,Fover social media posts in the UAE,
OL,10,Fsome of which have attracted
OL,11,Fwidespread attention.
OL,13,F"The family is extremely worried,"
OL,14,Fsaid Raphaella Stirling, a crisis
OL,15,Fmanager at Detained in Dubai.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,F"It's a natural reflex to photograph
OL,8,Fyour surroundings, but authorities are
OL,9,Fhypersensitive, and the real danger
OL,10,Fmay not be Iran's missiles overhead,
OL,11,Fbut the Emirati authorities' reaction
OL,12,Fto what people post online."
OL,14,FWatch: One example of footage of drone
OL,15,Fand missile strikes that have been
OL,16,Fwidely circulated on social media
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FDetained in Dubai says it is
OL,8,Fcontinuing to monitor the cases and
OL,9,Fworking to establish the full details
OL,10,Fof the allegations and the
OL,11,Fnationalities of the other individuals
OL,12,Fcharged.
OL,14,FThe statement comes as the conflict in
OL,15,Fthe Middle East continues, with Dubai
OL,16,Fbeing one of the countries in the
OL,17,Ffiring line.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
