OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FIn his first statement since becoming
OL,8,FIran's supreme leader, Ayatollah
OL,9,FMojtaba Khamenei said the regime will
OL,10,Fcontinue to target Gulf Arab
OL,11,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FAccording to the official case
OL,8,Fsummary, referenced by Detained in
OL,9,FDubai, those accused are alleged of
OL,10,Fhaving used an information network or
OL,11,Finformation technology tool to
OL,12,Fbroadcast, publish, republish, or
OL,13,Fcirculate false news, rumours, or
OL,14,Fprovocative propaganda that may incite
OL,15,Fpublic opinion or disturb public
OL,16,Fsecurity.
OL,18,F"The charges sound extremely vague but
OL,19,Fserious on paper," said Detained in
OL,20,FDubai CEO Radha Stirling.
OL,26,@{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,F"In reality, the alleged conduct could
OL,8,Fbe something as simple as sharing or
OL,9,Fcommenting on a video that is already
OL,10,Fcirculating online.
OL,12,F"Under UAE cybercrime laws, the person
OL,13,Fwho originally posts content can be
OL,14,Fcharged, but so can anyone who
OL,15,Freshapes, reposts or comments on it.
OL,16,FOne video can quickly lead to dozens
OL,17,Fof people facing criminal charges."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FPenalties in such cases can include up
OL,8,Fto two years in prison, fines ranging
OL,9,Ffrom AED 20,000 (around #4,000) to AED
OL,10,F200,000 (around #40,000), or both, and
OL,11,Fforeign nationals will also face
OL,12,Fdeportation.
OL,14,FMs Sterling noted that journalists
OL,15,Fhave travelled to Dubai specifically
OL,16,Fto film missile interceptions, sending
OL,17,Ffootage to editors abroad who then
OL,18,Fpublish it from outside the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,F"Once that material appears online,
OL,8,Fresidents and visitors inside the UAE
OL,9,Fwho share or comment on it could
OL,10,Fsuddenly find themselves accused of
OL,11,Fspreading rumours or damaging public
OL,12,Fsecurity.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
