PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,F"Foreigners need to understand that
OL,8,Fwhat may seem like normal social media
OL,9,Fbehaviour elsewhere can lead to arrest
OL,10,Fin the UAE," she said.
OL,12,FShe added that in some cases, people
OL,13,Fare treated as national security
OL,14,Fsuspects before the facts are
OL,15,Fclarified, meaning they can be taken
OL,16,Finto specialist facilities known for
OL,17,Fhuman rights abuses and held for
OL,18,Fextended periods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
