PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773349567
OL,3,CDubai: British tourist facing up to
OL,4,Ctwo years in prison over footage of
OL,5,Cmissiles
OL,7,FShe pointed to similar enforcement
OL,8,Facross the Gulf, including in Qatar,
OL,9,Fwhich has already charged more than
OL,10,F200 people under comparable laws
OL,11,Fduring the current regional tensions.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
